[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;36mв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;33m$ head -25 CLAUDE.md\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.030, "o", "@AGENTS.md\r\n\r\n# Harness Engineering Rules\r\n\r\nThis project uses **harness engineering** for autonomous AI development.\r\nAll rules are enforced automatically by pre-commit hooks. Violations block the commit.\r\n\r\n## Mandatory Rules (enforced by hooks)\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "1. **[BUILD-01] Compilation must pass** before commit (`./mvnw compile -q`)\r\n2. **[BUILD-02] All tests must pass** before commit (`./mvnw test`)\r\n3. **[BUILD-03] Code must be formatted** with Spotless (`./mvnw spotless:check -q`)\r\n4. **[QUAL-01] No System.out.println** вҖ” use `org.jboss.logging.Logger` only\r\n5. **[QUAL-02] No hardcoded secrets** вҖ” use `@ConfigProperty` or environment variables\r\n6. **[CONV-01] Conventional commits** вҖ” format: `type(scope): subject`\r\n7. **[CONV-02] Test coverage** вҖ” every `@Path` class must have a `*Test.java`\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nSee [CHECKLIST.md](CHECKLIST.md) for the complete verification checklist.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "## Self-Correction Protocol\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "When a commit is blocked by the harness:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "1. Read the HARNESS error message carefully вҖ” it lists ALL failures with rule IDs\r\n2. Fix ALL listed violations (not just the first one)\r\n"]
[4.005, "o", "\r\n"]
